            "Introduction to Cloud Computing",
            "Deployment Models: Public, Private, Hybrid",
            "Cloud Service Models: IaaS, PaaS, SaaS",
            "Overview of Azure Services",
            "Azure Global Infrastructure: Regions, Availability Zones, Edge Locations",
            "Azure Free Tier Overview"
          ],
          "handsOn": [
            "Explore Azure Portal",
            "Navigate Regions & Availability Zones",
            "Launch Free Tier Virtual Machine"
          ],
          "learningOutcome": "Understand Azure ecosystem and core cloud concepts"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "title": "Identity & Access Management (Azure AD)",
          "duration": "2 Days",
          "icon": "Shield",
          "topics": [
            "Users, Groups, Roles, Policies",
            "Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)",
            "Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA)",
            "Conditional Access Policies"
